list.abstract: terminal称为端子，一种电子元器件，用以导电和传导信号之用，分为昶升五金端子和五金塑胶端子。
《终点》（Terminal）是一部由沃恩·斯坦执导，玛格特·罗比、西蒙·佩吉、麦克·梅尔斯、马克斯·艾恩斯、德克斯特·弗莱彻等主演的科幻惊悚电影。该片于2018年5月11日在美国上映。

yingyinNormal.en: The program terminal from an ICBM missile...
To reach the terminal, you'll need to pass the main gates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要抵达这个终端计算机，你需要通过几扇设施大门。

yingyinNormal.en: And the only way to download the ledger is through the central computer terminal located there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下载这个账册的唯一方法就是通过那地方的中央计算机终端。

yingyinNormal.en: Electrical conduit? Bottom line is, there's no way into that terminal unless your profile is pre-installed in the security system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电缆导管呢？这是底线。要想进入终端，除非把你的个人资料提前存入安全系统。
你不认为我已无法挽留了？

yingyinNormal.en: Closer to earth is Grand Central Terminal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 靠近地面的是大中央车站。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, no, not at all, you're not terminal, you just, you just need some damage control.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不尽然，你并非无法挽留，我们只要防止事情恶化。

yingyinNormal.en: They wouldn't let us leave the terminal, so we slept next to these huge marble sculptures from Zimbabwe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不许离开航站楼 所以我们就睡在来自津巴布韦的巨型大理石雕塑边

yingyinNormal.en: Looks like Cleveland we're IFR, so we're gonna add them in to terminal constraints for IFR ceilings and VIS.
yingyinNormal.zh: 克利夫兰，我们在发传真，马上加入终点限制以及视觉识别系统。

yingyinNormal.en: She wasn't terminal, she wasn't sick. Her only rationale was... she was afraid of getting old. And losing control.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她没有危在旦夕，她没病她，这样做唯一的原因是她害怕变老…从而失去对一切的控制。

yingyinNormal.en: Go. London terminal is compromised. Repeat, London is compromised. Agent placed is down. Request immediate extraction.
yingyinNormal.zh: 说吧。伦敦分支遭遇入侵，重复，伦敦分支遭遇入侵，特工据点已经沦陷，请求允许立即撤离。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, well that's that lo-cal, non dairy, soy milk junk. We sort of, we save the real stuff for those really terminal cases.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为这是低卡无乳脂豆浆制的假冰淇淋，我们把真正的留到实在无法挽留了才吃。

yingyinNormal.en: Her final destination is Everett terminal. Frank Katulak manages the facility, keeping Boston fully supplied with natural gas.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最终目的地是埃弗雷特码头，弗兰克·卡特拉克管理，这些设备使波士顿的天然气供给充足。

yingyinNormal.en: So it's got to be one of the other two. Now, Howard, Howard's a lifelong drunk, pallor of his skin, terminal gin blossoms on his red nose. And, terror notwithstanding, a bad case of the DTs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一定是另外俩人中的一个。霍华德……霍华德终生酗酒，皮肤苍白，红鼻子尖有酒糟鼻。尽管吓人，但他患了酒毒性谵妄。

yingyinNormal.en: They all converge at America's busiest commuter hub, New York's Penn station, while only a few blocks away, trains from the north stream into another bustling train station, grand central terminal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们都在上班一族的中心点——拥聚一堂纽约的宾州车站就在几个街区以外,北方来的火车开向另外一个繁忙的车站纽约中央车站。
